Creating Date Table 10

Click on the icon for the Date Table measure.



To do Time Intelligence Functions, creating a date table is advisable; see below:

 9. Select the Modeling tab

10. New Table

11. Write the DAX Expression to create the table and press "Enter."

12. Go to the Field list and right-click on the Date table, and mark as Date Table.

13. A dialogue box appears, select Date and press ok.



14. Go to the Model View Page.

15. Make a relationship between the Date Table and Violence_Survey Table.
